       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           I D E N T I F I C A T I O N   D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       PROGRAM-ID. COB09100.
      ******************************************************************
      *
      *   Este programa carrega o Ficheiro COF09500 com os Projectos
      *   (COT36_PROJECTS) que:
      *     - estejam Activos (BACTIVE = "A");
      *     - que năo sejam Custos (ICTACUST = "N");
      *     - que possa ter horas (IACHORAS = "S");
      *     - que tenham horas introduzidas no Time Report do Ano/Męs
      *       anterior ao da data de processamento.
      *
      *     Para cada responsável que tenha endereço de email carregado,
      *     envia um Email com todos os projectos seleccionados desse
      *     responsável.
      *
      *     Para cada email enviado é gerado um ficheiro com a
      *     seguinte nomenclatura: COF95 + número sequencial com 5 pos.
      *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           E N V I R O N M E N T         D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                     CONFIGURATION SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       SPECIAL-NAMES. DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
      ******************************************************************
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                      INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT   COF09500-FILE
                    ASSIGN              TO DISK-COF09500
                    ORGANIZATION        IS SEQUENTIAL
                    FILE STATUS         IS VIAW0011-FSTATUS.

      ******************************************************************
       DATA DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   D A T A   D I V I S I O N                    *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                          FILE SECTION                          *
      ******************************************************************
       FD  COF09500-FILE.
           COPY COCF9500.

      ******************************************************************
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                    WORKING STORAGE SECTION                     *
      ******************************************************************
      * CONSTANTES
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-QCMDEXC          PIC  X(10) VALUE 'QCMDEXC'.
           05 CON-LENGTH           PIC S9(10)V9(5) COMP-3 VALUE 256.
           05 CON-SPACES           PIC  X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 CON-COF95            PIC  X(05) VALUE 'COF95'.
           05 CON-01               PIC  X(02) VALUE '01'.
           05 CON-12               PIC  9(02) VALUE 12.
           05 CON-SEP-PER          PIC  X(03) VALUE ' / '.
           05 WS-PROGNAME          PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COB09500'.
           05 WS-COCF9500          PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COF09500'.
           05 WS-ARVT0103          PIC  X(10) VALUE 'ARVT0103'.
           05 WS-COVT3605          PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT3605'.
           05 WS-COVT5303          PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT5303'.
           05 WS-COVT5101          PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT5101'.
           05 WS-COVT3401          PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT3401'.
           05 WS-HORAPROJ          PIC  X(10) VALUE 'HORAPROJ'.

      ******************************************************************
      * VARIAVEIS
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-FILE-NOME             PIC X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-FILE-NOME.
              10 WS-FILE-NOME-01       PIC X(05)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-FILE-NOME-02       PIC 9(05)  VALUE ZEROS.
      *
           05 WS-COMMAND               PIC X(256) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-EMAIL-TO              PIC X(200) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-EMAIL-CC              PIC X(200) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-EMAIL-BCC             PIC X(200) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-NUM-REG               PIC 9(05)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-RESP-ANT              PIC X(03)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DATA-HOJE             PIC X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-RESPONS               PIC 9(01)  VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-HORAS                 PIC 9(01)  VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-FECHADO               PIC 9(01)  VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-TOTHORAS              PIC S9(15)V99 COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
      *
           05 WS-DTMESANO              PIC X(10).
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DTMESANO.
              10 WS-DTMESANO-ANO       PIC 9(04).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-FIL1      PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-MES       PIC 9(02).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-FIL2      PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-DIA       PIC X(02).

      ******************************************************************
      * COPYS
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCL0001.
           COPY AQCW0109.
           COPY VIAL0015.
           COPY VIAW0011.
           COPY VIAW0012.
           COPY VIATK001.
           COPY VIATK002.
           COPY COCK0002.
           COPY ARCL2750.
           COPY ARCL5060.
      ******************************************************************
      * DB2
      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA       END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3605    END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3401    END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5303    END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5101    END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD0103    END-EXEC.

           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CRS_COT36 CURSOR FOR
                SELECT NIDPROJECTO
                     , CPROJECT
                     , GDESCPROJECT
                     , DBEGINDATE
                     , DENDDATE
                     , NPERCENTALERT
                     , DALERTDATE
                     , CMOEDA
                     , BACTIVE
                     , NBUDGET
                     , PAIS
                     , CLIENTE
                     , LINHANEG
                     , RESPONS
                     , IPROJI
                     , IPROJE
                     , IACHORAS
                     , IADESPESAS
                     , TPPFAT
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST
                     , TIPONEG
                     , DADJUDATE
                     , NBUDCTRV
                     , GJUSTORC
                     , COPORTUNITY
                     , DALTSTAT
                     , CEMPRESA
                     , ICTACUST
                  FROM COVT3605_PROJECTS
                 WHERE ICTACUST  = :COCD3605-ICTACUST
                   AND BACTIVE   = :COCD3605-BACTIVE
                   AND IACHORAS  = :COCD3605-IACHORAS
              ORDER BY RESPONS
                     , ICTACUST
                     , BACTIVE
                     , IACHORAS
                     , NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

      ******************************************************************
       01  FILLER              PIC X(40) VALUE 'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE'.
      ******************************************************************
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                        LINKAGE SECTION                         *
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCW0009.
      ******************************************************************
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING AQCW0009-DATA.
      ******************************************************************
      *              P R O C E D U R E   D I V I S I O N               *
      ******************************************************************
       0000-MAINLINE.
      ******************************************************************

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

      *--- Só executa se o periodo estiver aberto
           IF  AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
           AND WS-FECHADO = ZEROS
               PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
                  THRU 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0000-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           GOBACK.

      ******************************************************************
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA'      TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM AQCP0100-REG-INICIO
                 THRU AQCP0100-REG-INICIO-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM AQCP0100-OBT-DADOS-ARQ
                 THRU AQCP0100-OBT-DADOS-ARQ-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1100-OPEN-COCF9500
                 THRU 1100-OPEN-COCF9500-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE SPACES    TO WS-RESP-ANT.
           MOVE ZEROS     TO WS-NUM-REG.
           MOVE CON-COF95 TO WS-FILE-NOME-01.
           MOVE ZEROS     TO WS-FILE-NOME-02.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1200-WRITE-HEADER
                 THRU 1200-WRITE-HEADER-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1300-FORMATA-PER
                 THRU 1300-FORMATA-PER-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1400-LER-PER
                 THRU 1400-LER-PER-EXIT
           END-IF.

       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       1100-OPEN-COCF9500.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '1100-OPEN-COCF9500'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           OPEN OUTPUT COF09500-FILE.

           PERFORM 9030-FSCHECK
              THRU 9039-FSCHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN FS-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE WS-COCF9500            TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0011-FSTATUS       TO AQCW0100-FILE-STATUS
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       1100-OPEN-COCF9500-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       1200-WRITE-HEADER.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '1200-WRITE-HEADER'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * Preencher os titulos das colunas da tabela
           STRING 'Responsável;'            DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Projecto;'               DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Periodo;'                DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Total Horas'             DELIMITED BY SIZE
                                            INTO COCF9500-RECORD.

           WRITE COCF9500-RECORD.

           MOVE 1 TO WS-NUM-REG.

           PERFORM 9030-FSCHECK
              THRU 9039-FSCHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN FS-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE WS-COCF9500            TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0011-FSTATUS       TO AQCW0100-FILE-STATUS
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       1200-WRITE-HEADER-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       1300-FORMATA-PER.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '1300-FORMATA-PER '         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Formata Periodo do Ano/Męs anterior ŕ data de processamento
           MOVE ETCL0002-DATA-PROCESSO TO WS-DATA-HOJE.
      *
           MOVE WS-DATA-HOJE           TO WS-DTMESANO.
      *
           COMPUTE WS-DTMESANO-MES = WS-DTMESANO-MES - 1.

           IF WS-DTMESANO-MES = ZEROS
              MOVE CON-12              TO WS-DTMESANO-MES
              COMPUTE WS-DTMESANO-ANO = WS-DTMESANO-ANO - 1
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE CON-01                 TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA.
      *
       1300-FORMATA-PER-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       1400-LER-PER.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '1400-LER-PER     '         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *
      *--- Verifica se o periodo está fechado
      *
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO-ANO          TO COCD3401-ZANO
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO-MES          TO COCD3401-ZMES
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT CSITU
               INTO :COCD3401-CSITU
               FROM COVT3401_PERIODO
            WHERE ZANO     = :COCD3401-ZANO
              AND ZMES     = :COCD3401-ZMES
            FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-COVT3401              TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK AND COCD3401-CSITU = COCK0002-SITU-ABERTO
                 MOVE ZEROS TO WS-FECHADO
              ELSE
                 MOVE 1     TO WS-FECHADO
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
       1400-LER-PER-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2100-OPEN-CURSOR
              THRU 2100-OPEN-CURSOR-EXIT.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-FETCH-CURSOR
                 THRU 2200-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT

              PERFORM 2300-PROC-CURSOR
                 THRU 2300-PROC-CURSOR-EXIT
                      UNTIL NOT DB2-OK
                         OR NOT AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS

              IF  WS-RESP-ANT NOT = SPACES
              AND WS-NUM-REG > 1
                  PERFORM 2310-ENVIA-EMAIL
                     THRU 2310-ENVIA-EMAIL-EXIT
              END-IF

              EXEC SQL
                   CLOSE CRS_COT36
              END-EXEC
           END-IF.

       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2100-OPEN-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2100-OPEN-CURSOR'          TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE DCLCOCD3605.

           MOVE COCK0002-SIM            TO COCD3605-IACHORAS.
           MOVE COCK0002-NAO            TO COCD3605-ICTACUST.
           MOVE COCK0002-BACTIVE-ACTIVO TO COCD3605-BACTIVE.

           EXEC SQL
                OPEN CRS_COT36
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-COVT3605                 TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2100-OPEN-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2200-FETCH-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2200-FETCH-CURSOR'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                FETCH CRS_COT36
                 INTO :COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO
                    , :COCD3605-CPROJECT
                    , :COCD3605-GDESCPROJECT
                    , :COCD3605-DBEGINDATE
                    , :COCD3605-DENDDATE
                    , :COCD3605-NPERCENTALERT
                    , :COCD3605-DALERTDATE
                    , :COCD3605-CMOEDA
                    , :COCD3605-BACTIVE
                    , :COCD3605-NBUDGET
                    , :COCD3605-PAIS
                    , :COCD3605-CLIENTE
                    , :COCD3605-LINHANEG
                    , :COCD3605-RESPONS
                    , :COCD3605-IPROJI
                    , :COCD3605-IPROJE
                    , :COCD3605-IACHORAS
                    , :COCD3605-IADESPESAS
                    , :COCD3605-TPPFAT
                    , :COCD3605-CUSERID
                    , :COCD3605-HTIMEST
                    , :COCD3605-TIPONEG
                    , :COCD3605-DADJUDATE
                    , :COCD3605-NBUDCTRV
                    , :COCD3605-GJUSTORC
                    , :COCD3605-COPORTUNITY
                    , :COCD3605-DALTSTAT
                    , :COCD3605-CEMPRESA
                    , :COCD3605-ICTACUST
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-COVT3605                 TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2200-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2300-PROC-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2300-PROC-CURSOR'          TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Por cada Responsável de Projecto, envia um email
           IF WS-RESP-ANT = SPACES
              MOVE COCD3605-RESPONS TO WS-RESP-ANT
           END-IF.

      *    IF  WS-RESP-ANT NOT = COCD3605-RESPONS
      *    AND WS-NUM-REG  > 1
      *        PERFORM 2310-ENVIA-EMAIL
      *           THRU 2310-ENVIA-EMAIL-EXIT
      *        MOVE COCD3605-RESPONS TO WS-RESP-ANT
      *    END-IF.
      *
           IF WS-RESP-ANT NOT = COCD3605-RESPONS
              IF WS-NUM-REG  > 1
                 PERFORM 2310-ENVIA-EMAIL
                    THRU 2310-ENVIA-EMAIL-EXIT
              END-IF
              MOVE COCD3605-RESPONS TO WS-RESP-ANT
           END-IF.

      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
      *--- Acede ao COT53_PESSOAS para verificar se o responsável é
      *--- funcionário VIA (IVIA = "S")
      *---
      *--- Se năo encontrar ou IVIA <> "S" descarta o Projecto
      *---
      *--- Acede ao COT51_TIMEREPT Para ver se o projecto tem horas
      *--- inseridas para o periodo
      *---
      *--- Se năo encontrar horas para o projecto no periodo
      *--- descarta o Projecto
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2350-VER-RESPONS
                 THRU 2350-VER-RESPONS-EXIT

              IF WS-RESPONS = 1

                 IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
                    PERFORM 2351-VER-HORAS
                       THRU 2351-VER-HORAS-EXIT
                 END-IF

                 IF WS-HORAS = 1

                    INITIALIZE COCF9500-RECORD
                    MOVE ALL ';' TO COCF9500-RECORD

                    IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
                       PERFORM 2700-WRITE-COCF9500
                          THRU 2700-WRITE-COCF9500-EXIT
                    END-IF

                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-FETCH-CURSOR
                 THRU 2200-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2300-PROC-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2350-VER-RESPONS.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2350-VER-RESPONS   '       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCD3605-RESPONS     TO COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT NTRABALHADOR
                  , GNOME
                  , CUTILIZA
                  , IVIA
               INTO :COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR
                  , :COCD5303-GNOME
                  , :COCD5303-CUTILIZA
                  , :COCD5303-IVIA
               FROM COVT5303_PESSOAS
            WHERE NTRABALHADOR = :COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR
            FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-COVT5303         TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK AND COCD5303-IVIA = COCK0002-SIM
                MOVE 1     TO WS-RESPONS
           WHEN OTHER
                MOVE ZEROS TO WS-RESPONS
           END-EVALUATE.

       2350-VER-RESPONS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2351-VER-HORAS.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2351-VER-HORAS     '       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCD5101-CIDPROJ.
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO            TO COCD5101-DTMESANO.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT IFNULL(SUM(ZHORAS), 0)
               INTO :WS-TOTHORAS
               FROM COVT5101_TIMEREPT
            WHERE CIDPROJ  = :COCD5101-CIDPROJ
              AND DTMESANO = :COCD5101-DTMESANO
              AND ZHORAS   <> 0
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-COVT5101               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK AND WS-TOTHORAS NOT = ZEROS
                 MOVE 1        TO WS-HORAS
              ELSE
                 MOVE ZEROS    TO WS-HORAS
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2351-VER-HORAS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2700-WRITE-COCF9500.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2700-WRITE-COCF9500'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCD3605-RESPONS            TO COCF9500-RESPONS-COD.
           MOVE ' - '                       TO COCF9500-RESPONS-SEP.
           MOVE COCD5303-GNOME              TO COCF9500-RESPONS-DES.

           MOVE COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO        TO COCF9500-PROJECT-COD.
           MOVE ' - '                       TO COCF9500-PROJECT-SEP.
           MOVE COCD3605-CPROJECT           TO COCF9500-PROJECT-DES.

           MOVE WS-DTMESANO-ANO             TO COCF9500-ANO.
           MOVE CON-SEP-PER                 TO COCF9500-SEP.
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO-MES             TO COCF9500-MES.

           MOVE WS-TOTHORAS                 TO COCF9500-TOTAL.

           WRITE COCF9500-RECORD.

           COMPUTE WS-NUM-REG = WS-NUM-REG + 1.

           PERFORM 9030-FSCHECK
              THRU 9039-FSCHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN FS-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE WS-COCF9500            TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0011-FSTATUS       TO AQCW0100-FILE-STATUS
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2700-WRITE-COCF9500-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2310-ENVIA-EMAIL.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2310-ENVIA-EMAIL   '       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Fecha ficheiro
           CLOSE COF09500-FILE.

      *--- Copia ficheiro (cria ficheiro a enviar no email
      *--- apartir da cópia do ficheiro base)
           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2321-COPIA-FILE
                 THRU 2321-COPIA-FILE-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Envia Email
           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2320-ROT-EMAIL
                 THRU 2320-ROT-EMAIL-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Abre (e limpa) ficheiro base
           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1100-OPEN-COCF9500
                 THRU 1100-OPEN-COCF9500-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Escreve primeiro registo de cabeçalhos
           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1200-WRITE-HEADER
                 THRU 1200-WRITE-HEADER-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2310-ENVIA-EMAIL-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2321-COPIA-FILE.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2321-COPIA-FILE    '       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.
           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *-----------------------------------------------------*
      *--- Cria Nome Sequencial do Ficheiro (COF95nnnnn) ---*
      *-----------------------------------------------------*
           COMPUTE WS-FILE-NOME-02 = WS-FILE-NOME-02 + 1.

      *----------------------*
      *--- Copia Ficheiro ---*
      *----------------------*
           MOVE SPACES                     TO WS-COMMAND.
      *
           STRING
            'CPYF FROMFILE(*CURLIB/COF09500) TOFILE(*CURLIB/'
                                             DELIMITED BY SIZE
              WS-FILE-NOME                   DELIMITED BY SPACES
              ') MBROPT(*REPLACE) CRTFILE(*YES)'
                                             DELIMITED BY SIZE
                                             INTO WS-COMMAND.
      *
           CALL CON-QCMDEXC USING WS-COMMAND, CON-LENGTH.

       2321-COPIA-FILE-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2320-ROT-EMAIL.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2320-ROT-EMAIL     '       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.
           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2352-OBT-EMAIL
              THRU 2352-OBT-EMAIL-EXIT.

           IF WS-EMAIL-TO NOT = SPACES

              INITIALIZE ARCL2750-COMMAREA
              MOVE WS-HORAPROJ    TO ARCL2750-CCOD
              MOVE WS-EMAIL-TO    TO ARCL2750-CTO
              MOVE WS-EMAIL-CC    TO ARCL2750-CCC
              MOVE WS-EMAIL-BCC   TO ARCL2750-CBCC
              MOVE WS-FILE-NOME   TO ARCL2750-GNOMEFIC

              PERFORM ETCP0003-STD-INIT
                 THRU ETCP0003-STD-INIT-EXIT

              PERFORM CALL-ARM2750
                 THRU CALL-ARM2750-EXIT

              PERFORM ETCP0003-STD-END
                 THRU ETCP0003-STD-END-EXIT

              IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 CONTINUE
              ELSE
                 SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL       TO TRUE
                 MOVE WS-PROGNAME              TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                 MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID       TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                 PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                    THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2320-ROT-EMAIL-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2352-OBT-EMAIL.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2352-OBT-EMAIL     '       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.
           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *----------------------------------*
      *--- Busca responsável anterior ---*
      *----------------------------------*
           MOVE WS-RESP-ANT          TO COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR.
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT NTRABALHADOR
                  , GNOME
                  , CUTILIZA
                  , IVIA
               INTO :COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR
                  , :COCD5303-GNOME
                  , :COCD5303-CUTILIZA
                  , :COCD5303-IVIA
               FROM COVT5303_PESSOAS
            WHERE NTRABALHADOR = :COCD5303-NTRABALHADOR
            FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-COVT5303         TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

      *-------------------------------------------*
      *--- Busca email do responsavel anterior ---*
      *-------------------------------------------*
           MOVE  COCD5303-CUTILIZA    TO ARCD0103-GUSERNAME

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  GEMAIL
                  INTO :ARCD0103-GEMAIL
                  FROM  ARVT0103
                 WHERE  GUSERNAME = :ARCD0103-GUSERNAME
           END-EXEC.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF DB2-OK
               MOVE ARCD0103-GEMAIL TO WS-EMAIL-TO
             ELSE
               MOVE SPACES          TO WS-EMAIL-TO
               MOVE 'Utilizador năo tem email'
                                             TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
               MOVE 'ARCD0103-GUSERNAME   '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
               MOVE ARCD0103-GUSERNAME       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
               PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2352-OBT-EMAIL-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '3000-FIM-PROGRAMA'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           CLOSE COF09500-FILE.

      * Processos finais
            PERFORM AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE
               THRU AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT.

            PERFORM AQCP0002-TRATA-SYNCPOINT
               THRU AQCP0002-TRATA-SYNCPOINT-EXIT.

           PERFORM AQCP0100-REG-FIM
              THRU AQCP0100-REG-FIM-EXIT.

       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE AQCP0002 END-EXEC.
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCP0009.
           COPY AQCP0109.
           COPY VIAP0011.
           COPY VIAP0012.
           COPY VIAP0015.
           COPY ARCP2750.
      ******************************************************************
